# Telegram Anonymous Stranger Chat Bot

Production-ready foundation for a Telegram anonymous stranger chat bot built with Python 3.12+, aiogram 3.x, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Redis, SQLAlchemy 2.x, and Alembic.

## Features

- Registration with age, gender, nickname, preferred gender, interests, and consent.
- Anonymous 1:1 matchmaking with Redis-backed queueing and locks.
- Anonymous relay for text, photos, videos, voice notes, documents, and stickers.
- `/next`, `/end`, `/report`, `/profile`, `/cancel`, `/help`.
- Session transcript export to a private Telegram admin channel after chat end.
- Basic moderation with report flow and admin ban/unban/lookup commands.
- Dockerized deployment with FastAPI health checks and Nginx reverse proxy.

